Some examples of English main clause content questions are:
</introduction>
<EnglishExample>
	<exItem label="1.">Which boy hit the ball?</exItem>
	<exItem label="2.">Who hit the ball?</exItem>
	<exItem label="3.">Who might have hit the ball?</exItem>
	<exItem label="4.">What did the boy hit?</exItem>
	<exItem label="5.">Where is the leader?</exItem>
	<exItem label="6.">When will she come?</exItem>
</EnglishExample>
<prompt>Key similar examples from your language here:</prompt>
<textBox id="QContExample" dataItem="contentExample" cols="50"/>
<introduction>Examples of English embedded content questions include:</introduction>
<EnglishExample>
	<exItem label="1.">I know who hit the ball.</exItem>
	<exItem label="2.">I know when she will come.</exItem>
	<exItem label="3.">I know what the boy hit.</exItem>
</EnglishExample>
